hue - a posix shell script to control your philips hue lights

How to install
put the hue file into $PATH, that could be .local/bin or /usr/bin.

How to configure
read https://developers.meethue.com/develop/get-started-2/
the USER variable in .config/hue/conf should be the api key.
the IP variable should be the bridges ip, you can find this out by going onto your router/using nmap.